title: SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL
content:
0x79D3B596FE44EE8B0x2B39128B// SetVehicleDirtLevel
void SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL(Vehicle vehicle, float dirtLevel);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle to set.dirtLevel: A number between 0.0 and 15.0 representing the vehicles dirt level.Sets the dirt level of the passed vehicle.Examples:Lualocal Vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsUsing(PlayerPedId())
SetVehicleDirtLevel(Vehicle, 0.0) -- set the vehicle dirt level to 0.0

// SetVehicleDirtLevel
void SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL(Vehicle vehicle, float dirtLevel);

local Vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsUsing(PlayerPedId())
SetVehicleDirtLevel(Vehicle, 0.0) -- set the vehicle dirt level to 0.0
